{"id":658,"date":"2021-12-13T18:29:32","date_gmt":"2021-12-13T17:29:32","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/britonia.gal\/?page_id=658"},"modified":"2022-05-15T15:54:35","modified_gmt":"2022-05-15T13:54:35","slug":"ruta-augas-de-fonmina","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/britonia.gal\/ruta-augas-de-fonmina\/","title":{"rendered":"Ruta Augas de Fonmi\u00f1\u00e1"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>\u00ab(\u2026) Pssamos al rio famoso de nombre, \/ que en nuestra Galicia llamamos el Mi\u00f1o,\/ al qual hasta agora llamaramos ni\u00f1o,\/ mas otros que absorbe le hazen ser hombre,\/ en partes va bravo, que no ay quien no assombre, \/ passa por pueblos que aqu\u00ed se diran, \/ la fuente do nace se llama Mi\u00f1an, \/ que deste Mi\u00f1an tomo su renombre.\u00bb<\/p><p><\/p><cite>Bartolom\u00e9 Sagrario de Molina (1550),\u00a0<em>Descripci\u00f3n del Reyno de Galicia y de las cosas notables del<\/em>, M\u00e1laga, 4\u00aa parte, \u2018De los rios, y Pueblos\u2019, fol. 36<\/cite><\/blockquote>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Descubrindo Lugo: Ruta de Aguas de Fonmi\u00f1\u00e1 (A Pastoriza)\" width=\"950\" height=\"534\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/iNCad1fRHNc?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Esta ruta parte da Lagoa de Fonmi\u00f1\u00e1, sita xusto ao entrar no concello da Pastoriza polo Sur, vindo da carretera de Meira, e chega ata a praia fluvial de Baltar, na \u00e1rea recreativa de Liboira, pouco despois de pasar xunto ao Castro de Saa. Non \u00e9 unha ruta circular, polo que o percorrido de volta transcorre polo mesmo cami\u00f1o. O cami\u00f1ante non atopar\u00e1 grandes repechos ao longo dos 12 kil\u00f3metros e medio da ruta. A duraci\u00f3n estimada \u00e9 de 3 horas e 20 minutos.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>M\u00e1is informaci\u00f3n: <a href=\"https:\/\/es.wikiloc.com\/rutas-senderismo\/pr-g-153-augas-de-fonmina-12072201\">Wikiloc | Ruta PR-G 153 Augas de Fonmi\u00f1\u00e1<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/rutas.terrachanaturalmente.org\/gis\/index.php?concelloid=4&amp;nombre=Pastoriza&amp;rutaid=11\">Rutas de senderismo na Terra Ch\u00e1 (terrachanaturalmente.org)<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"713\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/britonia.gal\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/Ruta-Augas-de-Fonmina.-percorrido-713x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2121\" srcset=\"https:\/\/britonia.gal\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/Ruta-Augas-de-Fonmina.-percorrido-713x1024.jpg 713w, https:\/\/britonia.gal\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/Ruta-Augas-de-Fonmina.-percorrido-209x300.jpg 209w, https:\/\/britonia.gal\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/Ruta-Augas-de-Fonmina.-percorrido-768x1103.jpg 768w, https:\/\/britonia.gal\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/Ruta-Augas-de-Fonmina.-percorrido-8x12.jpg 8w, https:\/\/britonia.gal\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/Ruta-Augas-de-Fonmina.-percorrido.jpg 999w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 713px) 100vw, 713px\" \/><figcaption>M\u00e1is info na web: <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/www.turismo.gal\/recurso\/-\/detalle\/170526000720\/pr-g-153-augas-de-fomina?langId=es_ES&amp;tp=6&amp;ctre=23\" target=\"_blank\">https:\/\/www.turismo.gal\/recurso\/-\/detalle\/170526000720\/pr-g-153-augas-de-fomina?langId=es_ES&amp;tp=6&amp;ctre=23 <\/a><\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"312\" src=\"https:\/\/britonia.gal\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/Fonmina-A-PASTORIZA-1024x312.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1221\" srcset=\"https:\/\/britonia.gal\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/Fonmina-A-PASTORIZA-1024x312.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/britonia.gal\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/Fonmina-A-PASTORIZA-300x92.jpg 300w, https:\/\/britonia.gal\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/Fonmina-A-PASTORIZA-768x234.jpg 768w, https:\/\/britonia.gal\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/Fonmina-A-PASTORIZA-1536x469.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/britonia.gal\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/Fonmina-A-PASTORIZA-18x5.jpg 18w, https:\/\/britonia.gal\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/Fonmina-A-PASTORIZA.jpg 1898w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>\u00ab(\u2026) Pssamos al rio famoso de nombre, \/ que en nuestra Galicia llamamos el Mi\u00f1o,\/ al qual hasta agora llamaramos ni\u00f1o,\/ mas otros que absorbe le hazen ser hombre,\/ en partes va bravo, que no ay quien no assombre, \/ passa por pueblos que aqu\u00ed se diran, \/ la fuente do nace se llama Mi\u00f1an, &hellip; <\/p>\n<p class=\"link-more\"><a href=\"https:\/\/britonia.gal\/ruta-augas-de-fonmina\/\" class=\"more-link\">Read more<span class=\"screen-reader-text\"> &#8220;Ruta Augas de Fonmi\u00f1\u00e1&#8221;<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1221,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_mi_skip_tracking":false,"_EventAllDay":false,"_EventTimezone":"","_EventStartDate":"","_EventEndDate":"","_EventStartDateUTC":"","_EventEndDateUTC":"","_EventShowMap":false,"_EventShowMapLink":false,"_EventURL":"","_EventCost":"","_EventCostDescription":"","_EventCurrencySymbol":"","_EventCurrencyPosition":"","_EventDateTimeSeparator":"","_EventTimeRangeSeparator":"","_EventOrganizerID":[],"_EventVenueID":0,"_OrganizerEmail":"","_OrganizerPhone":"","_OrganizerWebsite":"","_VenueAddress":"","_VenueCity":"","_VenueCountry":"","_VenueProvince":"","_VenueZip":"","_VenuePhone":"","_VenueURL":"","_VenueStateProvince":"","_VenueLat":"","_VenueLng":""},"_links":{"s